structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
ORGANIZATION AND GOVERNMENT OF CITIES OF THE THIRD CLASS (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 434, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1980.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: City of third class may pay public funds to nonprofit hospital in city or county.
